name: No direct extraction possible
description: Direct extraction from the provided URL requires data access or structured metadata not available in the search results. However, for data catalogs in ArcGIS Hub, the metadata fields follow guidelines from the DCAT schema, and data owners and themes should be set according to the vocabularies you provided. To proceed with actual extraction, you need to access the catalog via API or structured feeds (e.g., data.json) as referenced in the ArcGIS documentation[2][3][4].
